years within 10 years within 20 years or is it farther off than 
that five 6 ten 29 twenty 26 farther off 28 dkna 11 
4 if there is another world war do you think it will escalate 
into an allout nuclear war or not yes 54 no 38 dkna 9 
5 do you sometimes think of germany as the enemy because of 
world war ii or do you think thats all behind us enemy 10 
behind 84 dkna 6 
