cattle futures prices fell sharply monday on the chicago 
mercantile exchange reflecting a seasonal slump in beef consumption 
during the dog days of summer 
on other markets coffee futures rebounded sugar futures 
declined grains and soybeans were mostly lower oil futures were 
mostly higher and precious metals retreated 
